Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Matt Barnes?

Matt Barnes is 45 years old.

Where was Matt Barnes born?

Matt Barnes was born in Santa Clara, California.

When was Matt Barnes born?

Matt Barnes was born on March 9, 1980.

How tall is Matt Barnes?

Matt Barnes is 6-7 (201 cm) tall.

How much did Matt Barnes weigh when playing?

Matt Barnes weighed 226 lbs (102 kg) when playing.

Is Matt Barnes in the Hall of Fame?

Matt Barnes is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Matt Barnes drafted?

Matt Barnes was drafted by Memphis Grizzlies, 2nd round (17th pick, 46th overall), 2002 NBA Draft.

What position did Matt Barnes play?

Small Forward and Power Forward.

When did Matt Barnes retire?

Matt Barnes last played in 2017.

What is Matt Barnes' net worth?

Matt Barnes made at least $35,675,098 playing professional basketball.

How much did Matt Barnes make?

Matt Barnes made $6,125,000 in 2017.

What did Matt Barnes average?

Matt Barnes averaged 8.2 points, 4.6 rebounds, and 1.8 assists per game.

How many rings does Matt Barnes have?

Matt Barnes won one championship.

What schools did Matt Barnes attend?

Matt Barnes attended Del Campo in Sacramento, California and UCLA.
